二手交易:
=========

获取分类列表
------------
/api1/business/sec/getcate?level=1
/api1/business/sec/getcate?level=2&pid=

gclist: [
{
  分类父id：pid
  分类id: id
  分类名: name
  分类全名: full_name
}
]

获取新旧列表
------------
/api1/business/sec/getnew



获取首页
--------
/api1/business/sec?type=0&page=1
/api1/business/sec?types=1&page=1
/api1/business/sec?types=2&page=1

type:分类，0 全部，1 求购列表, 2 转让列表
page:


发布帖子(post)
--------------
/api1/business/sec/post

cid=5284390201f5b411b4671cec
uid=52834bb61d41c80b4e0883a8
types: (1求购/2转让)
title:
content:
price:
new:新旧程度(1...9)
mobile:

搜索功能：
----------

